You must initialize EmojiCompat prior to referencing the EmojiCompat instance.

The most likely cause of this error is disabling the EmojiCompatInitializer
either explicitly in AndroidManifest.xml, or by including
androidx.emoji2:emoji2-bundled.

Automatic initialization is typically performed by EmojiCompatInitializer. If
you are not expecting to initialize EmojiCompat manually in your application,
please check to ensure it has not been removed from your APK's manifest. You can
do this in Android Studio using Build > Analyze APK.

In the APK Analyzer, ensure that the startup entry for

playstore_details.title: Blood Sugar Care & BP Monitor
playstore_details.description:
Your comprehensive heart health companion. Beyond accurate heart rate monitoring, Heart Rate & Al Health Tracker allows you to log and track other health metrics like blood pressure and blood sugar levels, providing a holistic view of your health.

——Overview of main functions:——

> Heart rate: Help you monitor your heart health at any time.
> Record blood pressure: Manage blood pressure health at any time.
> Record blood sugar: Regularly monitor blood sugar health.
> AI food recognition: accurately identify food and get the best recommendations.
> AI chat assistance: Instant, personalized lifestyle suggestions.
> Step tracking: Monitor your daily steps and achieve your fitness goals.
> Hydration tracker: Record your water intake.
> Weight management: Track your weight.
> Health articles: Get information about health, fitness, and wellness.

——Key Features:——

❤️ Heart rate monitoring and data analysis:
Real-time heart rate monitoring for early detection of potential issues.
Comprehensive data analysis to understand your heart health patterns.

🩸 Blood Pressure & Blood Sugar Management:
Effortless recording of blood pressure and blood sugar readings.
Visualize your data to identify trends and make informed decisions.

🍜Smart Nutrition Assistant
Your AI-powered food identifier! Snap a photo of your meal, and instantly get calorie counts, protein, fat, and more. Personalized nutrition tips based on your habits help you eat smarter. Download now and take control of your health!

🤖Unlock Your Personalized Health Insights with AI 
Get instant, tailored health advice from our AI Chatbot, and generate comprehensive health reports based on your unique body data. Experience the future of personalized wellness today!

🚶💦 Stay Active & Hydrated:
Integrated pedometer for step tracking and goal setting.
Personalized hydration reminders to ensure optimal water intake.

📈 Weight Management Made Easy:
Track your progress with daily or weekly weight recordings.
Receive expert-backed advice to achieve your weight goals.

📖 Stay Informed:
Access curated health articles on the latest trends and research.
Stay inspired with tips and motivation for a healthier lifestyle.

Download Heart Rate & Al Health Tracker today and take control of your health journey!

——Disclaimer:——

> Heart rate measurement results cannot replace the diagnosis of professional medical institutions. If you feel unwell, please seek medical attention in time. During the measurement process, different mobile devices may heat up to different degrees, so please be careful to prevent burns.

> The content generated by the AI ​​chat and suggestion functions is based on machine learning models and is for reference only. We are committed to providing accurate and useful information, but AI may occasionally produce inaccurate or misleading content.

If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us.
Email: ContactCenter@weather365d.com

Privacy Policy: https://weather365d.com/ailife/privacy-policy/
User Agreement: https://weather365d.com/ailife/terms-of-service/

hotspot.title: Found 6 critical permission(s)
hotspot.description:
Ensure that these permissions are required by the application.

android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION (dangerous): allow application to recognize physical activity - Allows an application to recognize physical activity.

android.permission.CAMERA (dangerous): take pictures and videos - Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION (dangerous): coarse (network-based) location - Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION (dangerous): fine (GPS) location - Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE (dangerous): read phone state and identity - Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS (dangerous): allows an app to post notifications. - Allows an app to post notifications
